1956;;Outside the Law;;American;;Jack Arnold;;Ray Danton, Leigh Snowden, Grant Williams;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Outside_the_Law_(1956_film);;A government agent's son, an ex-juvenile delinquent, is given the chance to prove himself when paroled from prison. He's given a mission to join the army to break up an international counterfeiting ring involving an ex- army friend. He has to woo his friend's girl and extract information from her.